Personal stories behind the news from all over the world. With Roger Hearing. Iranian militia, Martha Lane Fox, the Jews of Africa. Iranian Basij Journalist Lindsey Hilsum talks about her encounter with one of the Iranian militia blamed for increasingly brutal attacks on opposition protesters. Martha Lane Fox The dotcom pioneer on her part in internet revolution and surviving a serious car crash. Lemba Drum Steve Vickers has been to Harare to see the oldest wooden object ever found in sub-Saharan Africa, a sacred drum belonging to the people who call themselves the Jews of Africa Show less